{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1012,"text":"Cybercrime is out of control."},{"time":6186,"text":"It's everywhere."},{"time":7575,"text":"We hear about it every single day."},{"time":12771,"text":"This year,"},{"time":14009,"text":"over two billion records lost or stolen."},{"time":20050,"text":"And last year, 100 million of us,\nmostly Americans,"},{"time":25709,"text":"lost our health insurance data\nto thieves -- myself included."},{"time":32303,"text":"What's particularly concerning about this\nis that in most cases,"},{"time":37775,"text":"it was months before anyone even\nreported that these records were stolen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45164,"text":"So if you watch the evening news,"},{"time":48231,"text":"you would think that most of this\nis espionage or nation-state activity."},{"time":53993,"text":"And, well, some of it is."},{"time":56694,"text":"Espionage, you see, is an accepted\ninternational practice."},{"time":61793,"text":"But in this case,"},{"time":63300,"text":"it is only a small portion\nof the problem that we're dealing with."},{"time":69639,"text":"How often do we hear about a breach"},{"time":72998,"text":"followed by, \"... it was the result\nof a sophisticated nation-state attack?\""},{"time":78661,"text":"Well, often that is companies\nnot being willing to own up"},{"time":83546,"text":"to their own lackluster\nsecurity practices."},{"time":87065,"text":"There is also a widely held belief"},{"time":90355,"text":"that by blaming an attack\non a nation-state,"},{"time":94230,"text":"you are putting regulators at bay --"},{"time":96935,"text":"at least for a period of time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99837,"text":"So where is all of this coming from?"},{"time":104997,"text":"The United Nations estimates\nthat 80 percent of it"},{"time":110514,"text":"is from highly organized\nand ultrasophisticated criminal gangs."},{"time":117254,"text":"To date,"},{"time":118997,"text":"this represents one of the largest\nillegal economies in the world,"},{"time":125621,"text":"topping out at, now get this,"},{"time":128765,"text":"445 billion dollars."},{"time":133539,"text":"Let me put that in perspective\nfor all of you:"},{"time":136475,"text":"445 billion dollars is larger than the GDP"},{"time":142603,"text":"of 160 nations,"},{"time":145293,"text":"including Ireland, Finland,\nDenmark and Portugal,"},{"time":149862,"text":"to name a few."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152293,"text":"So how does this work?"},{"time":154321,"text":"How do these criminals operate?"},{"time":156701,"text":"Well, let me tell you a little story."},{"time":160531,"text":"About a year ago,"},{"time":161749,"text":"our security researchers were tracking"},{"time":165083,"text":"a somewhat ordinary but sophisticated\nbanking Trojan called the Dyre Wolf."},{"time":171925,"text":"The Dyre Wolf would get on your computer"},{"time":174170,"text":"via you clicking on a link\nin a phishing email"},{"time":177194,"text":"that you probably shouldn't have."},{"time":179170,"text":"It would then sit and wait."},{"time":181755,"text":"It would wait until you logged\ninto your bank account."},{"time":185299,"text":"And when you did,\nthe bad guys would reach in,"},{"time":188666,"text":"steal your credentials,"},{"time":190343,"text":"and then use that to steal your money."},{"time":193023,"text":"This sounds terrible,"},{"time":194967,"text":"but the reality is,\nin the security industry,"},{"time":197784,"text":"this form of attack\nis somewhat commonplace."},{"time":204002,"text":"However, the Dyre Wolf had\ntwo distinctly different personalities --"},{"time":210659,"text":"one for these small transactions,"},{"time":213024,"text":"but it took on an entirely\ndifferent persona"},{"time":216088,"text":"if you were in the business of moving\nlarge-scale wire transfers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219927,"text":"Here's what would happen."},{"time":221650,"text":"You start the process\nof issuing a wire transfer,"},{"time":224474,"text":"and up in your browser would pop\na screen from your bank,"},{"time":227506,"text":"indicating that there's a problem\nwith your account,"},{"time":230127,"text":"and that you need to call\nthe bank immediately,"},{"time":233342,"text":"along with the number\nto the bank's fraud department."},{"time":236835,"text":"So you pick up the phone and you call."},{"time":239029,"text":"And after going through\nthe normal voice prompts,"},{"time":242064,"text":"you're met with\nan English-speaking operator."},{"time":244205,"text":"\"Hello, Altoro Mutual Bank.\nHow can I help you?\""},{"time":248033,"text":"And you go through the process\nlike you do every time you call your bank,"},{"time":251710,"text":"of giving them your name\nand your account number,"},{"time":254525,"text":"going through the security checks\nto verify you are who you said you are."},{"time":259809,"text":"Most of us may not know this,"},{"time":261321,"text":"but in many large-scale wire transfers,"},{"time":263574,"text":"it requires two people to sign off\non the wire transfer,"},{"time":266709,"text":"so the operator then asks you\nto get the second person on the line,"},{"time":269932,"text":"and goes through the same set\nof verifications and checks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273960,"text":"Sounds normal, right?"},{"time":275909,"text":"Only one problem:"},{"time":277375,"text":"you're not talking to the bank."},{"time":279224,"text":"You're talking to the criminals."},{"time":280834,"text":"They had built\nan English-speaking help desk,"},{"time":283056,"text":"fake overlays to the banking website."},{"time":285145,"text":"And this was so flawlessly executed"},{"time":288269,"text":"that they were moving\nbetween a half a million"},{"time":290436,"text":"and a million and a half\ndollars per attempt"},{"time":293547,"text":"into their criminal coffers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296140,"text":"These criminal organizations operate"},{"time":298779,"text":"like highly regimented,\nlegitimate businesses."},{"time":302345,"text":"Their employees work\nMonday through Friday."},{"time":305309,"text":"They take the weekends off."},{"time":306869,"text":"How do we know this?"},{"time":308276,"text":"We know this because\nour security researchers see"},{"time":311433,"text":"repeated spikes of malware\non a Friday afternoon."},{"time":315254,"text":"The bad guys, after a long weekend\nwith the wife and kids,"},{"time":318493,"text":"come back in to see how well things went."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323701,"text":"The Dark Web is where\nthey spend their time."},{"time":327295,"text":"That is a term used to describe\nthe anonymous underbelly of the internet,"},{"time":333108,"text":"where thieves can operate with anonymity"},{"time":336057,"text":"and without detection."},{"time":338209,"text":"Here they peddle their attack software"},{"time":341260,"text":"and share information\non new attack techniques."},{"time":345571,"text":"You can buy everything there,"},{"time":347445,"text":"from a base-level attack\nto a much more advanced version."},{"time":351842,"text":"In fact, in many cases, you even see"},{"time":354158,"text":"gold, silver and bronze levels of service."},{"time":357903,"text":"You can check references."},{"time":359977,"text":"You can even buy attacks"},{"time":362561,"text":"that come with a money-back guarantee --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":365913,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":366982,"text":"if you're not successful."},{"time":369931,"text":"Now, these environments,\nthese marketplaces --"},{"time":373046,"text":"they look like an Amazon or an eBay."},{"time":376417,"text":"You see products, prices,\nratings and reviews."},{"time":380397,"text":"Of course, if you're going\nto buy an attack,"},{"time":382675,"text":"you're going to buy from a reputable\ncriminal with good ratings, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":386148,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":387176,"text":"This isn't any different"},{"time":388401,"text":"than checking on Yelp or TripAdvisor\nbefore going to a new restaurant."},{"time":394503,"text":"So, here is an example."},{"time":396620,"text":"This is an actual screenshot\nof a vendor selling malware."},{"time":402065,"text":"Notice they're a vendor level four,"},{"time":403904,"text":"they have a trust level of six."},{"time":405769,"text":"They've had 400 positive reviews\nin the last year,"},{"time":408128,"text":"and only two negative reviews\nin the last month."},{"time":411072,"text":"We even see things like licensing terms."},{"time":414762,"text":"Here's an example of a site you can go to"},{"time":416790,"text":"if you want to change your identity."},{"time":418571,"text":"They will sell you a fake ID,"},{"time":420452,"text":"fake passports."},{"time":422603,"text":"But note the legally binding terms\nfor purchasing your fake ID."},{"time":428518,"text":"Give me a break."},{"time":430063,"text":"What are they going to do --\nsue you if you violate them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":432945,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":435458,"text":"This occurred a couple of months ago."},{"time":437905,"text":"One of our security\nresearchers was looking"},{"time":441544,"text":"at a new Android malware application\nthat we had discovered."},{"time":446566,"text":"It was called Bilal Bot."},{"time":449514,"text":"In a blog post,"},{"time":451464,"text":"she positioned Bilal Bot\nas a new, inexpensive and beta alternative"},{"time":458870,"text":"to the much more advanced GM Bot"},{"time":462232,"text":"that was commonplace\nin the criminal underground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466658,"text":"This review did not sit well\nwith the authors of Bilal Bot."},{"time":471237,"text":"So they wrote her this very email,"},{"time":475028,"text":"pleading their case\nand making the argument"},{"time":477809,"text":"that they felt she had evaluated\nan older version."},{"time":484198,"text":"They asked her to please update\nher blog with more accurate information"},{"time":488931,"text":"and even offered to do an interview"},{"time":492367,"text":"to describe to her in detail"},{"time":494612,"text":"how their attack software was now\nfar better than the competition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500365,"text":"So look,"},{"time":501714,"text":"you don't have to like what they do,"},{"time":505602,"text":"but you do have to respect\nthe entrepreneurial nature"},{"time":510545,"text":"of their endeavors."}]},{"cues":[{"time":511776,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":514476,"text":"So how are we going to stop this?"},{"time":519714,"text":"It's not like we're going to be able\nto identify who's responsible --"},{"time":525302,"text":"remember, they operate with anonymity"},{"time":528288,"text":"and outside the reach of the law."},{"time":531217,"text":"We're certainly not going to be able\nto prosecute the offenders."},{"time":535156,"text":"I would propose that we need\na completely new approach."},{"time":541763,"text":"And that approach needs\nto be centered on the idea"},{"time":545693,"text":"that we need to change\nthe economics for the bad guys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550245,"text":"And to give you a perspective\non how this can work,"},{"time":553370,"text":"let's think of the response we see\nto a healthcare pandemic:"},{"time":558382,"text":"SARS, Ebola, bird flu, Zika."},{"time":562036,"text":"What is the top priority?"},{"time":563981,"text":"It's knowing who is infected\nand how the disease is spreading."},{"time":572015,"text":"Now, governments, private institutions,\nhospitals, physicians --"},{"time":579061,"text":"everyone responds openly and quickly."},{"time":583334,"text":"This is a collective and altruistic effort"},{"time":587329,"text":"to stop the spread in its tracks"},{"time":591253,"text":"and to inform anyone not infected"},{"time":594154,"text":"how to protect or inoculate themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598900,"text":"Unfortunately, this is not at all\nwhat we see in response to a cyber attack."},{"time":605850,"text":"Organizations are far more likely\nto keep information on that attack"},{"time":610325,"text":"to themselves."},{"time":613082,"text":"Why?"},{"time":614262,"text":"Because they're worried\nabout competitive advantage,"},{"time":618043,"text":"litigation"},{"time":619638,"text":"or regulation."},{"time":621827,"text":"We need to effectively democratize\nthreat intelligence data."},{"time":627975,"text":"We need to get all of these organizations\nto open up and share"},{"time":633475,"text":"what is in their private arsenal\nof information."},{"time":639010,"text":"The bad guys are moving fast;"},{"time":641828,"text":"we've got to move faster."},{"time":644750,"text":"And the best way to do that is to open up"},{"time":648496,"text":"and share data on what's happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651304,"text":"Let's think about this in the construct\nof security professionals."},{"time":656164,"text":"Remember, they're programmed right\ninto their DNA to keep secrets."},{"time":661164,"text":"We've got to turn\nthat thinking on its head."},{"time":664212,"text":"We've got to get governments,\nprivate institutions"},{"time":667517,"text":"and security companies"},{"time":668984,"text":"willing to share information at speed."},{"time":671739,"text":"And here's why:"},{"time":673439,"text":"because if you share the information,"},{"time":675340,"text":"it's equivalent to inoculation."},{"time":678663,"text":"And if you're not sharing,"},{"time":680234,"text":"you're actually part of the problem,"},{"time":682359,"text":"because you're increasing the odds\nthat other people could be impacted"},{"time":688151,"text":"by the same attack techniques."}]},{"cues":[{"time":691986,"text":"But there's an even bigger benefit."},{"time":695198,"text":"By destroying criminals' devices\ncloser to real time,"},{"time":699968,"text":"we break their plans."},{"time":703462,"text":"We inform the people they aim to hurt"},{"time":706726,"text":"far sooner than they had ever anticipated."},{"time":710520,"text":"We ruin their reputations,"},{"time":712745,"text":"we crush their ratings and reviews."},{"time":716305,"text":"We make cybercrime not pay."},{"time":720931,"text":"We change the economics for the bad guys."},{"time":726315,"text":"But to do this,\na first mover was required --"},{"time":730311,"text":"someone to change the thinking\nin the security industry overall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736067,"text":"About a year ago,"},{"time":737361,"text":"my colleagues and I had a radical idea."},{"time":740624,"text":"What if IBM were to take our data --"},{"time":745987,"text":"we had one of the largest threat\nintelligence databases in the world --"},{"time":749999,"text":"and open it up?"},{"time":751757,"text":"It had information not just\non what had happened in the past,"},{"time":755242,"text":"but what was happening in near-real time."},{"time":757741,"text":"What if we were to publish it all\nopenly on the internet?"},{"time":762463,"text":"As you can imagine,\nthis got quite a reaction."},{"time":764981,"text":"First came the lawyers:"},{"time":766369,"text":"What are the legal\nimplications of doing that?"},{"time":769385,"text":"Then came the business:"},{"time":770744,"text":"What are the business\nimplications of doing that?"},{"time":773622,"text":"And this was also met with a good dose"},{"time":775819,"text":"of a lot of people just asking\nif we were completely crazy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":779928,"text":"But there was one conversation\nthat kept floating to the surface"},{"time":783738,"text":"in every dialogue that we would have:"},{"time":786400,"text":"the realization that if we didn't do this,"},{"time":789971,"text":"then we were part of the problem."},{"time":793514,"text":"So we did something unheard of\nin the security industry."},{"time":797045,"text":"We started publishing."},{"time":798742,"text":"Over 700 terabytes of actionable\nthreat intelligence data,"},{"time":803176,"text":"including information on real-time attacks"},{"time":806205,"text":"that can be used to stop\ncybercrime in its tracks."},{"time":809813,"text":"And to date,"},{"time":811207,"text":"over 4,000 organizations\nare leveraging this data,"},{"time":815275,"text":"including half of the Fortune 100."},{"time":818599,"text":"And our hope as a next step\nis to get all of those organizations"},{"time":822640,"text":"to join us in the fight,"},{"time":824625,"text":"and do the same thing"},{"time":826200,"text":"and share their information"},{"time":828312,"text":"on when and how\nthey're being attacked as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":831552,"text":"We all have the opportunity to stop it,"},{"time":834594,"text":"and we already all know how."},{"time":837372,"text":"All we have to do is look\nto the response that we see"},{"time":841766,"text":"in the world of health care,"},{"time":843296,"text":"and how they respond to a pandemic."},{"time":845623,"text":"Simply put,"},{"time":847026,"text":"we need to be open and collaborative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":849876,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":851051,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}